<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<package xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/packaging/2012/06/nuspec.xsd">
  <metadata>
    <id>QuestPDF</id>
    <version>2024.10.2</version>
    <authors>MarcinZiabek</authors>
    <requireLicenseAcceptance>true</requireLicenseAcceptance>
    <license type="file">PackageLicense.md</license>
    <licenseUrl>https://aka.ms/deprecateLicenseUrl</licenseUrl>
    <icon>Logo.png</icon>
    <readme>PackageReadme.md</readme>
    <projectUrl>https://www.questpdf.com/</projectUrl>
    <iconUrl>https://www.questpdf.com/images/package-logo.png</iconUrl>
    <description>QuestPDF is an open-source, modern and battle-tested library that can help you with generating PDF documents by offering friendly, discoverable and predictable C# fluent API. Easily generate PDF reports, invoices, exports, etc.</description>
    <releaseNotes>Version 2024.10.0
- This version includes integration with the new QuestPDF Companion application.
- Updated the Skia dependency to version m130.
- Improved NuGet package determinism.
- Enhanced rendering of underline text decoration for certain fonts.


Version 2024.10.1
- Engine: Improved overflow annotation and layout algorithm for better handling of content overflow.
- Companion App: Enhanced message clarity regarding compatibility with merged documents.
- Companion App: Improved support for documents with multiple page configurations.
- Font discovery: Fixed file-access related exceptions.
- Font discovery: Improved default file path for font discovery.


Version 2024.10.2
- Fixed parsing of color values from both strings and uint.
- Fixed a rare memory leak issue occurring on certain CPU architectures.</releaseNotes>
    <copyright>Marcin Ziąbek, QuestPDF contributors</copyright>
    <tags>PDF C# dotnet csharp .NET PDF library PDF document PDF generation PDF creation PDF report PDF invoice PDF export windows linux mac azure aws open-source open source free adobe file SVG HTML XPS</tags>
    <repository type="git" url="https://github.com/QuestPDF/library.git" commit="9b6f99f40dc7c49b829d1384fb2c2406fb445e6f" />
    <dependencies>
      <group targetFramework="net6.0" />
      <group targetFramework="net8.0" />
      <group targetFramework=".NETStandard2.0" />
    </dependencies>
  </metadata>
</package>